{"tid":1567452,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果良心大發iPhone 11系列配置6GB記憶體？！想太多了！","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:52:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":53,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"75f9d3530885d15e4f013daf5b24fc6d35f20655","tid":1567452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"對蘋果來說，其習慣是不拼規格（處理器除外），所以發表會上很少公布iPhone的具體配置，特別是記憶體、電池容量等關鍵訊息。<br />\n<br />\n今日，OneLeaks爆料稱iPhone 11系列最高配置了6GB記憶體，可惜這是錯誤的，依舊是4GB而已。雖然沒有拆解，但是最近iPhone 11三款機種的跑分早就出現於Geekbench 4資料庫中了，其識別出來的訊息較個人的爆料是更可靠的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/002-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F002-7.jpg&h=13ce71c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone 11的跑分訊息顯示記憶體為3834MB，亦即是4GB容量，較iPhone XR倒是提升了1GB。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 11 Pro的跑分資訊如下，記憶體是3759MB，亦為4GB而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 11 Pro Max呢？會不會良心一點？可惜並沒有，資訊顯示記憶體依然是4GB。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從Geekbench 4顯示的資訊來看，iPhone 11系列所謂的6GB記憶體應是謠傳，電池容量尚不確定，而4GB記憶體估計有段時間裡是不會增加了，不然下幾代iPhone怎麼辦？"},{"pid":"0e9364b8d8680bfc9840c2249f95f5afe55c5e73","tid":1567452,"uid":234159,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6v9Jdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6v9Jdp.jpg&h=6cbe719f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFtYML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFtYML.jpg&h=a79b44b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa2d38905d2760de9aae0f2ba2e76995eb1d6b50","tid":1567452,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/apple/69616/apple-iphone-11-ram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link